{
  "texts": [
    "Instead, the words within one single line in the image are divided into multiple rows in the OCR-processed text.",
    "The lack of correct structure in OCR-converted text poses a significant challenge for information extraction using LLMs as it requires LLMs to have advanced understanding capability to analyze the overall text.",
    "To improve performance, more advanced computer vision approaches should be applied for text conversion, which is beyond the scope of this paper.",
    "Once we have converted the text information, the next step is to feed it into a pre-designed prompt for LLM for extracting well location and depth.",
    "LLMs are machine learning models trained on vast amounts of data."
  ]
}